        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Our 14 oz Disposable Kraft Paper Charcuterie Cups are crafted from high-quality, durable kraft paper with an internal lining to prevent moisture absorption, ensuring sturdiness even with greasy or saucy foods. Designed for easy handling, they’re perfect for serving appetizers, veggies, desserts, or popcorn at parties, weddings, baby showers, outdoor picnics, Christmas, anniversaries, grand openings, or company picnics. The disposable design makes cleanup effortless, letting you focus on enjoying the event. These eco-friendly cups offer a stylish, practical serving solution for both casual and formal occasions. Customizable with logos for wholesale or promotional needs, they’re available in various sizes—contact customer service for details. Rush service is also offered to meet tight deadlines.",
